Language: uz

00:00:00.430 --> 00:00:04.712
Yaxshi, demak, endi biz ViewGroup lar qanday qilib 
 view lardan tashkil topa olishini bilamiz.

00:00:04.712 --> 00:00:08.050
Har bir ViewGroup ning uning 
ichidagi farzandlarini qanday qilib 

00:00:08.050 --> 00:00:09.270
joylashtirish bo‘yicha maxsus qoidalar bor.

00:00:09.270 --> 00:00:11.292
Birinchi, keling, Linearlayout ga qaraymiz.

00:00:11.292 --> 00:00:15.120
Bu ViewGroup farzandlarini vertikal ustunda 
mana bunday qilib tartibga solib chiqishi mumkin.

00:00:17.310 --> 00:00:20.990
Biz qanday qilib faqatgina bitta textView va 
bittagina ImageView ga cheklanmaganimizni esga oling.

00:00:20.990 --> 00:00:25.200
Biz ulardan o‘zimiz xohlaganimizcha bu yerga qo‘ya 
olamiz shuningdek view larning boshqa turlarini ham.

00:00:25.200 --> 00:00:27.220
Demak, bu Tommy va u Timmiyning akasi.

00:00:27.220 --> 00:00:30.426
Va bu Ivy, u Irenaning egizak opasi.

00:00:30.426 --> 00:00:35.780
Yoki LinerLayout uning farzand 
 view larini mana bunday qilib 

00:00:35.780 --> 00:00:36.410
gorizontal chiziqda tartiblay oladi.

00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:41.140
Hoy, agar siz o‘g‘il bolalarga ro‘xsat berilmaydiku, 
deyayotgan bo‘lsangiz, bu menga mutlaqo mumkin.

00:00:42.240 --> 00:00:45.140
Bu Ivy, Irena va Isabella.

00:00:45.140 --> 00:00:47.630
Yaxshi, bu LinearLayout uchun hammasi shu.

00:00:47.630 --> 00:00:48.880
Yetarlicha bevosita, to‘g‘rimi?

00:00:48.880 --> 00:00:52.225
Siz farzandlarni vertikal ustunda yoki 
gorizontal qatorda tartiblay olasiz.

00:00:52.225 --> 00:00:54.847
Undan keyin bizda ota, ya‘ni RelativeLayout bor.

00:00:54.847 --> 00:00:55.985
 RelativeLayout ni ham 
uning ichidagi bolalarini 

00:00:55.985 --> 00:00:58.575
qanday qilib joylashtirish 
bo‘yicha shaxsiy qoidalari bor.

00:00:59.575 --> 00:01:03.545
Misol uchun u farzandlarni otaga 
nisbatan joylashtira oladi.

00:01:03.545 --> 00:01:05.455
Shunday qilib, agar u ota ViewGroup bo‘lsa,

00:01:05.455 --> 00:01:09.040
bizda otaning pastki qismiga joylashtirilgan 
 TextView bo‘la oladi va 

00:01:09.040 --> 00:01:12.270
bitta farzand, ImageView otaning 
yuqori qismiga joylashtirilsa bo‘ladi.

00:01:12.270 --> 00:01:14.380
Bu yana otaning chap va o‘ng 
qirralariga shuningdek 

00:01:14.380 --> 00:01:16.060
markaziga joylashtirish 
uchun ham ishlaydi.

00:01:17.330 --> 00:01:19.870
 RelativeLayout ning boshqa 
bir foydali qobiliyati bu 

00:01:19.870 --> 00:01:23.531
siz farzandlarni boshqa farzand view larga 
nisbatan joylashtirib chiqa olasiz.

00:01:23.531 --> 00:01:25.960
Shunday qilib, agar bu 
ota ViewGroup bo‘lsa, 

00:01:25.960 --> 00:01:30.310
unda siz bironta ImageView ni 
otaning chap tomoniga va 

00:01:30.310 --> 00:01:33.760
undan so‘ng bironta TextView ni o‘sha 
rasmning o‘ng tomoniga joylashtira olasiz.

00:01:33.760 --> 00:01:37.780
Va shundan so‘ng, bu farzand, TextView , 
 ImageView ning o‘ng tomoniga ammo, 

00:01:37.780 --> 00:01:40.680
birinchi TextView dan 
pastga joylashtirililadi.

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:44.690
Demak, siz bu farzand view lar 
qanday qilib otaga yoki bir-biriga

00:01:44.690 --> 00:01:46.100
nisbatan joylashtirilayotganini ko‘rib turibsiz.

00:01:47.210 --> 00:01:50.990
Bu rostdan ham RelativeLayout ning 
 LinearLayout ga qarshi qisqacha tavsifi edi.

00:01:50.990 --> 00:01:53.870
Siz dasturingiz uchun xohlayotgan layoutning 

00:01:53.870 --> 00:01:55.620
turiga bog‘liq bo‘lgan boshqalarini qanday 
qilib tanlab olishni ko‘rishingiz mumkin.

00:01:56.640 --> 00:02:00.190
Hozir, qanday qilib ViewGroup boshqa view lardan 
tashkil topishi haqidagi XML kodni ko‘rib chiqamiz.

00:02:01.330 --> 00:02:02.050
Bu misolda,

00:02:02.050 --> 00:02:06.060
ikkita farzand TextView dan tashkil 
topadigan ViewGroup dan boshlaymiz.

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:09.300
Bu biz odatlanganimizdagidan 
ko‘ra biroz ko‘proq kod, 

00:02:09.300 --> 00:02:12.350
ammo men sizni bu kod haqida ba‘zi o‘rganishlar 
qilib chiqiqshingizni xohlardim.

00:02:12.350 --> 00:02:17.370
Ishora sifatida, ota kodi qizilda, va 
farzand TextView kodi ko‘kda.

00:02:17.370 --> 00:02:20.030
Biz bu kodga quyida havola berganmiz va shunday ekan, 

00:02:20.030 --> 00:02:21.740
siz unga qarab chiqa olasiz va shunda bu yerga 
uchta kuzatuv natijangizni yozib qo‘ying.

